# 🚀 Meta-Learning / Controller-Selection Extension — TODOs

This extension asks a new question on top of the current paper:

> **Given a new environment (alpha engine + universe + regime structure), can we identify the best controller without exhaustively running all candidates?**

This is a **meta-learning / algorithm-selection** direction and can significantly strengthen the paper’s novelty if implemented cleanly.

